  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    ErrorResponse
    The ErrorResponse class is a simple data transfer object (DTO) that encapsulates error message information.
    LoginDTO
    The LoginDTO class represents a data transfer object for user login information.
    QuestionDTO
    The QuestionDTO class serves as a general data transfer object for questions, supporting different types of questions like text, slide, and true or false.
    QuizDTO
    The QuizDTO class is a data transfer object that encapsulates the data of a quiz.
    RegisterDTO
    The RegisterDTO class represents a data transfer object for user registration.
    SlideAnswerDTO
    The SlideAnswerDTO class represents a data transfer object for answers that are based on a sliding scale.
    SlideQuestionDTO
    The SlideQuestionDTO class extends QuestionDTO to represent a question that requires a sliding scale answer.
    SubmitAnswerDTO
    The SubmitAnswerDTO class is a simple data transfer object used for submitting answers to questions.
    SubmittedAnswerDTO<T>
    The SubmittedAnswerDTO class is a generic data transfer object used for representing the result of a submitted answer.
    TextAnswerDTO
    The TextAnswerDTO class represents a data transfer object for text-based answers.
    TextQuestionDTO
    The TextQuestionDTO class extends QuestionDTO to represent a question that has text-based answers.
    TrueOrFalseAnswerDTO
    The TrueOrFalseAnswerDTO class represents a data transfer object for answers to true or false questions.
    TrueOrFalseQuestionDTO
    The TrueOrFalseQuestionDTO class extends QuestionDTO to represent a question that can be answered with either true or false.
    UserDTO
    The UserDTO class represents a data transfer object for user information.
